video_title: Will you put it into practice? #inspiration #mindset #adviceoftheday #positivity
transcript:
get away from people who talk to
you distance yourself from those people
who aren't doing anything with their
lives remove people who aren't following
their dreams I don't care if it's your
best friend your family your parents if
someone is toxic to you or constantly
talking down to you they are killing
your dreams and study show that being
around toxic people actually kills you
quicker learn to surround yourself with
people who are good for you and good for
your future and most importantly good
for your mental health
